headline: MSCI Announces the Results of the MSCI 2025 Global Market Accessibility Review
summary: NEW YORK, June 19, 2025--MSCI Inc. (NYSE: MSCI), a leading provider of critical decision support tools and services for the global investment community, announced today the results of the MSCI 2025 Global Market Accessibility Review. The detailed report, covering market accessibility assessments for 86 markets, has been made available on www.msci.com/market-classification.
